<TR><TD BACKGROUND="/pics/pageback2.jpg" ALIGN="CENTER" CLASS="pagename">Tips zum "Iksar Necromancer"</TD></TR>
<TR><TD HEIGHT="3" BACKGROUND="/pics/line0.jpg"><IMG SRC="/pics/temppx.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="3" ALT=""></TD></TR>
